## ğŸ§ª CLI Usage

```bash
python main.py path/to/dataset.csv target_column_name
```

### Optional flags:

* `--output_dir`: Folder to save results (default: `results`)
* `--pca_components`: Apply PCA on numeric features
* `--no_shap`: Disable SHAP plot (faster)

